----------------------------------------README for Assigment 7-----------------------------------

(THERE ARE SAMPLE INPUT AND OUTPUT IN SUBMISSION FOLDER. OUTPUT IMAGE NAME CLEARLY MENTION WHAT OPERATION IS APPLIED ON THEM)

1. To run the program for this assignment go to folder and type following on terminal:
	for filters:
		"python hough_transformation.py standard_test_images/[Image_Name]"
		
2. This will run the program and will show the output of hough transformation. Two options for steps of theta and r will be taken as input:
	a. Type step theta (delta theta) for r-theta space : 
	b. Type step r (delta r) for r-theta space : 
3. After saving the image it will show output and ask for rerun the program:
		Press 'q' to quit  : 
		Press Enter to run again:                                               ____Enter
	
4. go to standard_test_images_Hough_Transformed to see segmented images. In this folder images has extension about what operation is done on them (with paramters)	
	For each images there is a image created. 
	a. extension for file is _hough_transformed
			
For any doubt or query mail at taruny@iitrpr.ac.in
